    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Save the file using &lt;strong&gt;:wq&lt;/strong&gt; and exit from the text editor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can perform the above steps for domain2 also, only we have to create a file on domain2.com location as given below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt; [root@Microhost]# vi /var/www/domain2.com/public_html/index.php &lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
